{"tid":827524,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日比車撞 終於體驗到死前嘅一刻...","createTime":"2018-09-19T03:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T08:17:06.000Z","uid":98507,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1bd0adf63591f0caad3fe960975016ee813af883","tid":827524,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"話說尋日行過醫院嘅停車場入口<br />\n咁梗係望右邊睇下有冇車出<br />\n見冇車我咪行<br />\n行左第1步<br />\n對面線本應入去嘅的士狗竟然唔入<br />\n突然轉彎走人...<br />\n一野隊埋黎我度<br />\n嗰刻 睇野好慢好慢好慢<br />\n仲有時間比我心諗 係咪有走馬燈呢？<br />\n一諗完 我雙手撳左落佢車頭<br />\n佢都同時踩break<br />\n手腕一陣劇痛<br />\n<br />\n原來...係冇走馬燈嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一回神即刻屌柒個的士狗<br />\n佢又真係成隻狗咁係度遞晒手扮冇事<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母岩岩先係醫院出黎<br />\n轉個頭又要返入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1c5ba8ee98c04cc5e0ea5a4b1077e9672a93b8","tid":827524,"uid":146769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"你應該即係尼馬式插水"},{"pid":"91d53dc69927fa5c5ae997c79c1db185e7f87ac0","tid":827524,"uid":146769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你應該即刻尼馬式插水</blockquote>"},{"pid":"941d5bd7b6e8934bf35ea25b24987ca3606f73a4","tid":827524,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91d53dc69927fa5c5ae997c79c1db185e7f87ac0","tid":827524,"uid":146769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你應該即刻尼馬式插水</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"碌返入去醫院"},{"pid":"7133d2e6083e5b9ffa72158dd31970dbb46c4698","tid":827524,"uid":2223,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"應該要咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mlahotels.com/uploadfile/2015/12/9/20151231014514292.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlahotels.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2015%2F12%2F9%2F20151231014514292.gif&h=0b